<figureCitation id="9C6A15392A859824031E17F0A7607552" captionStart="Figure 35" captionStartId="F35" captionText="Figure 35. Aloe pruinosa. Photo: N. R. Crouch." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.142.48365.figure35" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/388261" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">35</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
